source: Παρατηρουμε πως σε ολες τις πολεις της Ελλαδας η υψηλοτερη θερμοκρασια παρατηρειται το 2013 και η χαμηλοτερη τον 18ο αιωνα .Αυτο σημαινει πως η θερμοκρασια εχει αυξηθει σε μεγαλο βαθμο τα τελευταια χρονια , επιβεβαιωνεται λοιπον η υπερθερμανση του πλανητη

max_min_list = []
countries = temp_by_country['Country'].unique()

for country in countries:
    curr_temps = temp_by_country[temp_by_country['Country'] == country]['AverageTemperature']
    max_min_list.append((curr_temps.max(), curr_temps.min()))
    
# thetoume metavlites 
res_max_min_list = []
res_countries = []

for i in range(len(max_min_list)):
    if not np.isnan(max_min_list[i][0]):
        res_max_min_list.append(max_min_list[i])
        res_countries.append(countries[i])

    #upologizoume tis diafores thermokrasion     
differences = []

for tpl in res_max_min_list:
    differences.append(tpl[0] - tpl[1])
    
#taksinomoume tis xores
differences, res_countries = (list(x) for x in zip(*sorted(zip(differences, res_countries), key=lambda pair: pair[0], reverse=True)))

#tropopoioume to diagramma 
f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 8))
sns.barplot(x=differences[:15], y=res_countries[:15], palette=sns.color_palette("coolwarm", 25), ax=ax)

texts = ax.set(ylabel="", xlabel="Temperature difference", title="Countries with the highest temperature differences")
plt.show()

countries = np.unique(temp_by_country['Country'])
mean_temp = []
for country in countries:
    mean_temp.append(temp_by_country[temp_by_country['Country'] == 
                                               country]['AverageTemperature'].mean())

#tropopoioume to 3d diagramma 
    
data = [ dict(
        type = 'choropleth',
        locations = countries,
        z = mean_temp,
        locationmode = 'country names',
        text = countries,
        marker = dict(
            line = dict(color = 'rgb(0,0,0)', width = 1)),
            colorbar = dict(autotick = True, tickprefix = '', 
            title = '# Average\nTemperature,\n°C')
            )
       ]
#thetoume tis metavlites toys diagrammatos 
layout = dict(
    title = 'Average land temperature in countries',
    geo = dict(
        showframe = False,
        showocean = True,
        oceancolor = 'rgb(0,255,255)',
        projection = dict(
        type = 'orthographic',
            rotation = dict(
                    lon = 60,
                    lat = 10),
        ),
        lonaxis =  dict(
                showgrid = True,
                gridcolor = 'rgb(102, 102, 102)'
            ),
        lataxis = dict(
                showgrid = True,
                gridcolor = 'rgb(102, 102, 102)'
                )
            ),
        )

fig = dict(data=data, layout=layout)
py.iplot(fig, validate=False, filename='worldmap')
